  <summary date="2020-02-21T19:17:09Z" status="Introduced in House">Chief Manufacturing Officer Act

This bill directs the President to appoint a United States Chief Manufacturing Officer who shall (1) coordinate manufacturing-related policies and activities across agencies; and (2) create and submit a national manufacturing srategy to develop the manufacturing sector, encourage economic growth, and promote the competitiveness of U.S. manufacturing.</summary>
